HEADWORD: Capsquare
<hw>Cap"*square</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Gun.)</fld>
<def>A metal covering plate which passes over the trunnions of a cannon,
and holds it in place.</def>⟦br⟧
